{"id": 3005, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都会在哪些时刻意识到“自己被流行影响了”？", "description": "欢迎分享那些“说不清流行是啥，但却意外发现自己正身处流行当中”的瞬间。（题图来自：iStock ©️ bulentgultek）", "record_count": 8755, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201909191845055kBuaWIwhz4nScit.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-19T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5921, "title": "你都会在哪些时刻意识到“自己被流行影响了”？", "content": "你都会在哪些时刻意识到“自己被流行影响了”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 346891, "content": "虽然不喜欢流行语，说话的时候偶尔还是会冒出几句", "image": "img/option/option/20190919175251JxiUWqRdlKjmCnVc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346892, "content": "平时很少刻意听神曲，却意外发现每首都能跟着哼几句", "image": "img/option/option/20190919175502LSFlZuodk0DY5Gyj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346894, "content": "本来觉得某种时尚不好看，流行久了就觉得顺眼很多", "image": "img/option/option/20190919175851Yd7JIFZNELDni0sa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346895, "content": "原本不太需要的商品，被反复种草就变成了必需品", "image": "img/option/option/20190919183929qe8chTaHxOsNp6w5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346896, "content": "尽管并没有很想去网红店，还是不能免俗地打了卡", "image": "img/option/option/20190919185057aj1s36YvkxUNJ2XH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346898, "content": "在某个问题上需要意见，会习惯性先看 KOL 们的观点", "image": "img/option/option/20190919181631YUed7xqVWPnMt52z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346900, "content": "明明从来没追过星，却能一眼认出当红明星们的脸", "image": "img/option/option/2019091918275174JZXLG89V2eEiSd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346901, "content": "平时不怎么刷社交媒体，但对热点新闻还是一清二楚", "image": "img/option/option/20190919183047b7C3UKpmTO8DcIQ4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346903, "content": "以上都没有，流行对我好像没啥影响", "image": "img/option/option/20190919183429YBf8FL6PyNRdMamQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}